Edge cases:
- Every component ID must be globally unique within the page
- picsum.photos URLs use seed for deterministic images
- Button onClick is a function prop - JSON pages cannot set functions, so Button rendered from JSON will not fire onClick but will render correctly visually
- Custom bullet styles (check/arrow/dot) use listStyleType none and render the symbol as a span prefix
- Gradient divider colors (blue-gradient, green-gradient, purple-gradient, rainbow) are read via colorMap in Divider.js, they override the variant to produce a linear-gradient background instead of a border
- AlertBox onClose prop is a function, same limitation as Button onClick - renders but no handler
- Grid autoFit/autoFill use CSS repeat(auto-fit/auto-fill, minmax(minItemWidth, 1fr))
- Section title/subtitle are rendered by the Section component itself (not children)
- Image component uses img tag directly, not wrapped in a container

